just_use helpers.go

# label: CLEAN_INFRA
# role: encodes domain knowledge

Shared primitives for the tricks package. extractCard is the load-bearing
one: it encodes the three legal peel shapes (end-peel on a 4+ stack; set-
peel of any middle card of a 4+ SET; middle-peel of a run when both halves
would be ≥ 3). Returns a new board rather than mutating — divergence from
TS's in-place mutation that simplifies atomic Apply semantics.

substituteInStack, pushNewStack, freshlyPlayed, singleStackFromCard are
straightforward wrappers that keep individual trick files uncluttered.
